      <hedline>
        <hl1>Euro RSCG Buys Internet Specialist</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Stuart Elliott</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Elliott, Stuart</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Euro RSCG Worldwide acquires Middleberg &amp; Associates, public relations agency specializing in Internet clients; financial terms undisclosed (Advertising column) (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Euro RSCG Worldwide in New York, part of Havas Advertising, said yesterday that it had acquired Middleberg &amp; Associates in New York, a public relations agency specializing in Internet clients. Terms were not disclosed.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Euro RSCG Worldwide in New York, part of Havas Advertising, said yesterday that it had acquired Middleberg &amp; Associates in New York, a public relations agency specializing in Internet clients. Terms were not disclosed.</p>
        <p>Middleberg has 150 employees and billings estimated at more than $22 million from clients like I.B.M. and the United Airlines unit of the UAL Corporation. The agency, which will be renamed Middleberg Euro RSCG, will operate autonomously and serve as the foundation of an expansion to North America by the Euro RSCG international communications group. Don Middleberg, 54, will continue as chief executive.</p>
        <p>THE MEDIA BUSINESS: ADVERTISING -- ADDENDA</p>
      </block>
